name: AS_GSS_UT_duplicateEvaluatorTeams
description: Duplicate evaluator team details from existing evaluation.
sail_code:
a!localVariables(
  local!sourceEvaluationTeams: rule!AS_GSS_QE_getEvaluatorTeam (
    returnType: cons!AS_CO_ENUM_QE_RETURN_TYPE_OBJECT_ARRAY,
    evaluationId: ri!evaluationId
  ),
  #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_forEach"(
    local!sourceEvaluationTeams,
    'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:GSS}AS_GSS_EvaluatorTeam'(
      teamId: fv!index,
      teamName: fv!item.teamName,
      teamDescription: fv!item.teamDescription,
      isActive: true
    )
  )
)
